---
title: Palak’s South Indian Shrimp Curry with Coconut Milk and Basmati Rice
description: “Take a trip to Southern India with my mouthwatering shrimp stew! Creamy coconut milk is infused with rich aromas from curry, tomatoes, onions, and garam masala, making this a decadent dish. These flavors will transport you to the tranquil backwaters of Kerala where the cuisine is as colorful as the region.” –Chef Palak
